#  Guest List Manager

A simple, responsive single-page web application that lets you manage a guest list for any event. Add, edit, categorize, and mark attendance status for up to 10 guests.

## Features
1. Add a guest with a name and category (Friend, Family, or Colleague)
2. Edit guest names inline
3. Toggle attendance status (Attending / Not Attending)
4. Remove guests from the list
5. Color-coded category tags
6. Stylish, user-friendly interface
7. Max 10 guests allowed

## Built With

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla)

##  Getting Started

1. Clone or download the repository.
2. Open `index.html` in your browser.

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/guest-list-manager.git
cd guest-list-manager
open index.html  # or simply double-click the file


